<p>They again set out on foot with one luggage in hand, and are greeted by a kind stranger in military uniform who pulls beside them in a truck. </p>

<p>Wilmer Valderrama cameos as the stranger who tells them he's heading toward a 'hot meal,' if they want to join, and he takes them to his home where he is greeted by his wife and two children. </p>

<p>Justin, Ryan and Wilmer's family end the video around the table holding hands to pray. </p>

